      "mediumTitle": "NVIDIA\u0027s KV Cache Pruning",
      "longTitle": "KVzap: Reducing LLM Memory Footprint",
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "Lines": [
            "NVIDIA AI has open-sourced KVzap to",
            "address the increasing KV cache size in",
            "transformer decoders.",
            "Pruning the KV cache makes large",
            "language models more practical for",
            "real-world applications.",
            "The substantial memory footprint of the",
            "KV cache hinders the deployment of LLMs",
            "with extended context windows.",
            "KVzap delivers near-lossless",
            "compression, meaning minimal performance",
            "impact from the size reduction.",
            "The KV cache size is a significant issue",
            "for deploying large models like",
            "Llama1-65B.",
            "The KV cache stores keys and values in",
            "the shape (2, L, H, T, D) for each layer",
            "and head.",
            "This new method is designed to tackle",
            "the bottleneck of KV cache size."
          ]
        }
      ],
